/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac371fbd3f2575c0f911a7d3be2943674d8643c","tid":218690,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9做到更多小城同埋加媾女就好<br />\n<br />\n仲有城耐久度高應該愈高防至係<br />\n升爆都無用嘅，下下俾人飛射連弩屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n錢糧太多要再調整<br />\n徵哂兵役會加不滿，容易造反、收成商業下降<br />\n<br />\n加埋青州兵虎豹騎江東軍無當軍呢啲特式兵種就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地形加成</blockquote><br />\n希望14係咁"},{"pid":"a172f9bb0f23ed1edb674d85f633f18c731b81bc","tid":218690,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>9做到更多小城同埋加媾女就好<br />\n<br />\n仲有城耐久度高應該愈高防至係<br />\n升爆都無用嘅，下下俾人飛射連弩屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n錢糧太多要再調整<br />\n徵哂兵役會加不滿，容易造反、收成商業下降<br />\n<br />\n加埋青州兵虎豹騎江東軍無當軍呢啲特式兵種就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地形加成</blockquote><br />\n希望14係咁</blockquote><br />\n除左溝女呢個point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd4b7440f9e13ba1c9ab358b49d5e16e8f1758b","tid":218690,"uid":29085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"各位大哥 跪求9的dl link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6fbed268513201e5f77a5337975d8e71188e0f","tid":218690,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位大哥 跪求9的dl link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得我係用個乜鳩exe安裝程式既，好似大概係san9pk v5咁上下，二三百mb左右，巴打搵搵有冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23d54122704d0d1c07bedfecb602fadfd84bc67","tid":218690,"uid":72773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"１１pk版好正 一坐城玩死種田 升曬三級市場農田徵兵訓練所 <br />\n<br />\n先再打下一坐城 又再升過 無限loop<br />\n<br />\n唔夠打就狂起箭樓城牆卡位玩TD<br />\n<br />\n不過比人打爆基建好撚唔爽 <br />\n<br />\n仲記得打公孫度好似可以打爆個水壩玩水攻<br />\n<br />\n諗起扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cafaf73d930c2814b2fc41cbbdc8b98e8834af","tid":218690,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三國志六愛好者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edd86780517e4f2c6641e23dafb995324ca5c32","tid":218690,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"三國9刷外族傷兵 其實幾易玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19de3c15e53828fa97aa25ec2c42309ee206cbc0","tid":218690,"uid":67347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三國志六愛好者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六我就最鐘意佢個單挑"},{"pid":"ec7cf7f196314b8da995423741c2d237f1b8153f","tid":218690,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三國9刷外族傷兵 其實幾易玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係大國咪易玩<br />\n當你係小國，下下俾佢屈錢，打佢但人地啲戰法又屈<br />\n慢慢磨你，又俾其他國打就輸㗎啦"},{"pid":"552f0753a72a8009875e0d5b00b11c22974bf7fc","tid":218690,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dis