集<br />\n攻城路線/守城配置對戰果既影響力大於武將能力/士兵數量<br />\n最重戰略味既戰棋game<br />\n戰鬥節奏快但不失玩味（當然你果隊全神將另計）<br />\n以弱勝強靠埋伏，戰爭迷霧去佔人據點<br />\n真正做到0交鋒而屈人之兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攻城時亦要防範電腦一樣咁樣做而要周圍搵敵軍或者留部隊守據點<br />\n唔係場場allin晒沖出去就鸁<br />\n加強版仲有武將傳<br />\n場場要你超劣勢黎打<br />\n諗起都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四聖獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d004835627402622949612cc27e7790c5fb10313","tid":218690,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"跪求9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要window 10玩到既<br />\n<br />\n之前down過好多 大陸個d一係有毒 一係win10 玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5520ed6b9ccb6d9ab8d03b33238d10bf9b71a6b0","tid":218690,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bcbec64768064ff8e55b3bfa689a0fc4f4ba5f7","tid":218690,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"由三國志7開始到三國志9每集都有玩，但真係只有９同１１會不停重玩"},{"pid":"f61f4216f1b75c2b2a7f5793587823e3c9153b44","tid":218690,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dee1d3a9349dc739ae3a0ecd5cb7ae522043d408","tid":218690,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"如果將鋼鐵雄心玩法整落去應該唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafa38ba7b9798993ac246731dccdcab3abccd44","tid":218690,"uid":86037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim